opptjening.title: Your pension earnings
opptjening.intro_text: Here you will find a comprehensive overview of your pension earnings. You can earn pension rights up to and including the year you turn 75. If you turned 13 in 2010 or later, you can earn from the year you turned 13. If you were 17 years or older in 2010, you can earn from the year you turned 17.
